## STAGE 7-8: CAM OUTPUT VALIDITY
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

PRE-CAM GENERATION GATE (all must pass before LLM call):
  □ All CRITICAL violations resolved
  □ All documents have validation_status = 'approved'
  □ All 7 ratios computed for at least 2 of 3 years
  □ Five Cs scores recomputable (L-1, L-2, L-3 checks pass)
  □ Override audit trail complete (L-4)
  □ At least 1 source_document_id per CAM section has traceability to page

POST-CAM VALIDATION:
  - Every figure cited in CAM must have a source:
    → Find all numbers in CAM text
    → Each must trace to: source_document_id + page OR computed_financial_ratios row
    → Untraceable figures → flag for manual review before export
  - SWOT quadrants must each have at least 1 bullet point
  - Each SWOT bullet must link to at least 1 underlying signal or data point
  - Recommendation decision (Approve/Reject/etc.) must match computed decision band
  - "What would change this decision" section must be non-empty for all non-Approve decisions

